00:45:26.900 --> 00:45:29.230
that I'm presenting to today.

00:45:29.230 --> 00:45:33.387
It's not the audience that
I get at universities.

00:45:33.387 --> 00:45:35.220
It's not the audience
that I get at meetings

00:45:35.220 --> 00:45:37.700
of the World Archaeological
Congress or European

00:45:37.700 --> 00:45:40.200
Association of Archaeologists.

00:45:40.200 --> 00:45:41.470
A good question.

00:45:41.470 --> 00:45:43.980
And I'm writing a
book to answer it.

